column1: ; Output of running w3stringsx on the example2_input directory.
; Script will resursively search for .xml and .ws files to parse for string keys.
; This mod used the ibt_ prefix to identify its strings, but there are some cases like `panel_Mods` that doesn't adhere to it.
; That's where we can use regex to our advantage.
; So to parse the directory we execute: python w3stringsx.py example2_input/ --search "(ibt_
